==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: xerophyte
<hw>xe"ro*phyte</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A plant adapted
for life with a limited supply of water; compare
<contr>hydrophyte</contr> and <contr>mesophyte</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> desert plant, xerophytic plant, xerophile,
xerophilous plant.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>xerophytic</ent>⟦br⟧
